    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randotura is a top-down action roguelike with inventory management.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Creation:</strong> In Randotura, the power of level design is in your hands. Place shop, combat and bonus rooms to strategically shape your adventure. Every decision you make influences the game’s difficulty and flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense Combat:</strong> Dodge enemy projectiles and weave between their attacks. Randotura has a variety of enemies with distinct behaviour to challenge your bullet hell skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Upgrades:</strong> All upgrades in Randotura have a significant impact—no boring stat changes! But beweary since cost of an item is its place on the map. Combine these upgrades to tailor your playstyle, creating devastating combos.</p>",
